'From Squeak4.3 of 22 December 2011 [latest update: #11860] on 19 August 2012 at 4:20:23 pm'!"Change Set:		CharacterLeadingCharCodeRevert-muDate:			19 August 2012Author:			Masashi UmezawaReverted Character>>leadingChar: leadChar code: code. Hoping it is temporary"!!Character class methodsFor: 'instance creation' stamp: 'ar 4/9/2005 22:24'!leadingChar: leadChar code: code	code >= 16r400000 ifTrue: [		self error: 'code is out of range'.	].	leadChar >= 256 ifTrue: [		self error: 'lead is out of range'.	].	^self value: (leadChar bitShift: 22) + code.! !